\imt1 Asulumaęž‰noęž‰ towoęž‰ we
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ ene ao nowoęž‰, Yaęž‰maęž‰s koęž‰loęž‰ e saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Yaęž‰su e henfeloęž‰ amioęž‰ siaęž‰len amioęž‰, ene ao iyaęž‰yoęž‰ e moęž‰tilidaęž‰daki, emoęž‰woęž‰ dioęž‰ge saęž‰laęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega tif amioęž‰ Yaęž‰maęž‰s e tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, saęž‰s boęž‰foęž‰lowan kalu alan nowoęž‰ e koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰.
\ip Moęž‰foęž‰s we Yaęž‰maęž‰s, e saęž‰saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ sab oęž‰moęž‰ iligaęž‰feloęž‰. Moęž‰foęž‰s eloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ wenamioęž‰, to alande Yaęž‰maęž‰s eloęž‰ widoęž‰woęž‰ we.
\ip Keliso kalukaęž‰isale ni amioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, tilidabu nilidoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ domaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰.
\ip Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalu oęž‰liaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalu oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ idaęž‰nika tilidomaęž‰ki saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Nowoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki, nowoęž‰ dianilaęž‰soęž‰bo. Niliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ asuwaęž‰talega, nili tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ hendele aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ kalaba widakigab.
\ip Nioęž‰ megoęž‰foęž‰ dinafa tilidowakiyoęž‰, Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au dimidaki, e haęž‰ga domaęž‰ki, saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰. Yaęž‰maęž‰s eyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wemaęž‰ man oęž‰liaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene man oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ alobana boęž‰baęž‰ki, fanda widoęž‰.
\ip Yaęž‰maęž‰s eyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we halaidoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ Yaęž‰su amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ e madalileyoęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰bakaęž‰. Kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale nolboęž‰woęž‰ man nafa dimidab aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, enen tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ halaidoęž‰kaęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰liki widab.
\c 1
\s1 Moęž‰foęž‰s Yaęž‰maęž‰saęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 1.1 \xt Madi 13.55, Ilig 15.13, Gala 1.19, 1Bid 1.1\x*Ne Yaęž‰maęž‰s, Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ Yaęž‰su Keliso Alan oęž‰liaęž‰maęž‰ ene madali nanogdoęž‰ dian kaluwoęž‰ ne. Niyoęž‰ moęž‰foęž‰s we, Keliso kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ soęž‰loęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰\f + \fr 1.1 \ft Yaęž‰maęž‰s eyoęž‰ â€śsoęž‰loęž‰ kugulaęž‰foęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ iasi kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ tambowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ sioęž‰.\f* alobanagaęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ hen no amiloęž‰ mesaęž‰ni ane gimoęž‰woęž‰ sagaloęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ligaęž‰toęž‰l.
\s1 Daęž‰fe baęž‰dab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ niyoęž‰ halale alitab
\p 
\v 2-3 \x - \xo 1.2-3 \xt Lom 5.3-5\x*\x - \xo 1.2-3 \xt 1Bid 1.7\x*Ni nao i, daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ giloęž‰ amiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, gili tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ anayaki, gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kagamaęž‰kigab. Aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ asulufoęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, daęž‰fe baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, gioęž‰ sagalaęž‰bi.
\v 4 Gioęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kagataęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, gili tilidabuwoęž‰ ilili alifaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, hidaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ giliyoęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lubi.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 1.5 \xt Sndn 2.3-6\x*Gi amioęž‰ kalu imilise nowoęž‰ asugoęž‰ nafayoęž‰ e amioęž‰ aundoęž‰ma dowalega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode Eyoęž‰ moęž‰gadi saęž‰laki, sagalaęž‰liki modoęž‰ aęž‰dimiaęž‰sen koęž‰loęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ dabu baęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ hendele diaęž‰ib.
\v 6 Koęž‰sega Godemoęž‰ dabu baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ nemoęž‰woęž‰ hendele dimiaęž‰ib aęž‰laęž‰tili asulaki dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, dulugu saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, i hidoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fufayaęž‰ baęž‰lab amiloęž‰ diaęž‰sianoęž‰ aęž‰gaęž‰lab.
\v 7 Kalu oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, Alan Eyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ nowoęž‰ kalu emoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰nigab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 8 Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ dowakiyoęž‰, eloęž‰ man aęž‰dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ babale domaęž‰ib.
\s1 Kalu kelegoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma oęž‰liaęž‰ kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰
\p 
\v 9 Keliso kalukaęž‰isale kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma dowab aęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰bi, moęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰ iyoęž‰ wabulun kalukaęž‰isale dowab.
\v 10 \x - \xo 1.10 \xt Ais 40.6-7\x*Koęž‰sega kalukaęž‰isale kelegoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ sagalaęž‰bi, moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ haęž‰ga domaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰lab. Mamo koęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰e udu haęž‰nan aumboęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale i aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ kelegemaęž‰ib.
\v 11 Hendele, ofoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ taęž‰ndab amioęž‰, mamo momadoęž‰ nafa aęž‰noęž‰ onaliaki, udufoęž‰ tinan. Oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale kelegoęž‰woęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰, ene nanog aęž‰noęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, eloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ kelegemaęž‰ib.
\s1 Kaluloęž‰ daęž‰fe baęž‰baęž‰noęž‰ to
\p 
\v 12 Kalukaęž‰isale daęž‰feyoęž‰woęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ wi amiloęž‰ halale kagayab aęž‰noęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ sagale alifaęž‰ib. Moęž‰woęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale eloęž‰ alan asulab oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dinali sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, daęž‰fe baęž‰baęž‰ amioęž‰ iyoęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kagayalikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ dimiakiyoęž‰, melaęž‰noęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib. \fig Kalukaęž‰isale daęž‰feyoęž‰ amiloęž‰ halale kagayab aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ waęž‰loęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib.|alt="Man wearing a crown" src="BK00158B.TIF" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles revised by Louise Bass Â© The British & Foreign Bible Society, 1994." ref="1.12"\fig*
\p 
\v 13 Kelegoęž‰ imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiyoęž‰ moęž‰sendeaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiyoęž‰, moęž‰dikidaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ asulalikiyoęž‰, â€śAęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ ne mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidamaęž‰ki sendeabâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 14 Koęž‰sega mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰kiloęž‰ dikili baęž‰danoęž‰ we. Kalukaęž‰isaleyaęž‰ asuloęž‰ us amiloęž‰ meselan delen aęž‰maęž‰ sendeliaęž‰gaęž‰ ogaęž‰di alitaęž‰sen.
\v 15 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ meselan aęž‰maęž‰ fowoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ helemaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ man mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰ alan dowaliki fo hedakiyoęž‰, man mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ sowanoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 16 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni milile, gioęž‰ halaloęž‰ asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 17 Boba kelegoęž‰ nafale nilidoęž‰ diab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ yan. Gode eyoęž‰ akin amiloęž‰ hoęž‰len daęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ tambo eya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰do alifaęž‰. Akin amiloęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, sololi faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega Gode enenoęž‰ e melaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰ngoęž‰ aęž‰lab.
\v 18 \x - \xo 1.18 \xt Yoęž‰n 1.13\x*Gode eyoęž‰ enedoęž‰ asulab au dimidakiyoęž‰, nioęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ dimaęž‰ki, to hendele enedoęž‰maęž‰ sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, nioęž‰ ene soęž‰wale dowab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kelegoęž‰ tamboloęž‰ dimidalifaęž‰ aęž‰lab us aęž‰namioęž‰, nioęž‰ waęž‰laęž‰b koęž‰loęž‰ taęž‰foęž‰.
\s1 Towoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi
\p 
\v 19 Ni milile, giliyoęž‰ to we asulaęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ tambo kalu nolbaęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰laboęž‰ dinafa daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ haęž‰sa saęž‰laęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ boęž‰boęž‰geboęž‰ gadiaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1.20 \xt Sav 7.9\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ gadialikiyoęž‰, man digaloęž‰woęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab aumboęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰sen.
\v 21 \x - \xo 1.21 \xt Kolo 3.8, 1Bid 2.1\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ asuloęž‰ usamiloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gaęž‰lilaki dilaęž‰bi. Dilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰ga iliki, Godeyaęž‰ ene to gili kufaęž‰ usamiloęž‰ diaęž‰tab aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa tilidaęž‰daęž‰bi. To halaidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gioęž‰ oęž‰li gasiliaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 1.22 \xt Madi 7.26, Lom 2.13\x*Giliyoęž‰ towoęž‰ ba madali daęž‰dalega, ginin aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dikidab koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ dimidaęž‰soęž‰bo. Gioęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, dinafa kudu haęž‰naęž‰lubi.
\v 23-24 Kalu abeyoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ towoęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰kudu haęž‰nab aęž‰noęž‰, kalu ene woęž‰lokanoęž‰ hewoęž‰ amiloęž‰ baęž‰baęž‰ oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab. Kalu aęž‰noęž‰ ene woęž‰lokanoęž‰ hewoęž‰wa baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nakiyoęž‰, wigibo aęž‰naka gaęž‰lilaęž‰sen.
\v 25 \x - \xo 1.25 \xt Lom 8.2, Yaęž‰m 2.12\x*Koęž‰sega Godeyaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ nafale daęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ gaęž‰li meseaęž‰ki taęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ to aęž‰noęž‰ dinafa asulufoęž‰likiyoęž‰, to eloęž‰ daęž‰dab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰gaęž‰lilaki, eyoęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰lalega, Gode eyoęž‰ e asuwaęž‰taki, eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ nafale aęž‰taęž‰faęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 26 \x - \xo 1.26 \xt Song 141.3\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ â€śNe Gode hendeleyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kudu haęž‰naęž‰senâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰asulaęž‰li koęž‰sega, ene megoęž‰foęž‰ dinafayoęž‰ moęž‰tili dowalega, e enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dikidab koęž‰loęž‰ ene tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab.
\v 27 Do Godeyaęž‰ siwaęž‰l amioęž‰, tilidabuwoęž‰ digaloęž‰ dowakiloęž‰ man hendele dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ we. Ga saęž‰baęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ dabusoęž‰ soęž‰wa oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ diab amioęž‰ dinafa tilidowan. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ wemaęž‰yoęž‰ eyamioęž‰ heyoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰domaęž‰ki, gaęž‰li saęž‰sen.
\c 2
\s1 Gioęž‰ noloęž‰ gola baęž‰dakiyoęž‰, dianilaęž‰soęž‰bo
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 2.1 \xt Ilig 10.34, Yaęž‰m 2.9\x*Ni mili, gioęž‰ Alan Yaęž‰su Keliso maliloęž‰ e amioęž‰ tilidabu koęž‰loęž‰, kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ nafale aęž‰laęž‰ alobaęž‰dakiyoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ noloęž‰ dianilaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 2-4 Gioęž‰ toloęž‰ widaęž‰sen aya kegeakiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalu nowoęž‰, helebesoęž‰goęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ momadoęž‰woęž‰ nafale kagedelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ mesaęž‰ni mioęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalu nowoęž‰ helebesoęž‰goęž‰ heyoęž‰ kataęž‰gaęž‰ mesaęž‰ni mioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, giyoęž‰ wabulun kaluwoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki, â€śge uwoęž‰b nafa wena meseaâ€ť aęž‰laki, koęž‰sega kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalu oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ â€śge faęž‰s dobaęž‰daęž‰ mesaęž‰ hamanaâ€ť moęž‰ â€śge haęž‰laęž‰ya kagafoęž‰meleaâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰lalega, goęž‰noęž‰n kele asuloęž‰ mogagoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰ ilikiyoęž‰, kaluwoęž‰ aęž‰na alobaęž‰dakigab.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 2.5 \xt 1Kol 1.26-28\x*Ni milile, gioęž‰ dabuma. Henfeloęž‰ wenamioęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ ini tilidabuwoęž‰ alan domaęž‰ki, Gode eyoęž‰ iyoęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tamin amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ â€śkalu abeyoęž‰ ne alan asulalega, amisaęž‰n niloęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lab aęž‰namioęž‰ tinaęž‰ibâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰dinali sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰goęž‰ kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalukaęž‰isale i wemaęž‰ ti hamanaęž‰ki, Godeyaęž‰ daęž‰feyoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 6-7 Koęž‰sega gililoęž‰ man dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, kelegoęž‰loęž‰ma kalu aęž‰noęž‰ dianilakigab. Gioęž‰ asulaęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ abe waęž‰laęž‰ saęž‰ndanoęž‰? Gioęž‰ abe moęž‰walilanoęž‰? Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Yaęž‰suwaęž‰ wi nafa gililoęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰ abe dioęž‰ge saęž‰laęž‰lenoęž‰? Kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalu iliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidaęž‰sen.
\p 
\v 8 \x - \xo 2.8 \xt Madi 19.19, Gala 5.14\x*Godeyaęž‰ to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ amioęž‰, nili misaęž‰ kalu Gode eloęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰ â€śGioęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰n asulan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, giasi kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰asulaki haęž‰foęž‰woęž‰ disaęž‰laęž‰bi.â€ť Aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ ele aęž‰noęž‰ hendele kudu haęž‰nalega, gioęž‰ digaloęž‰ dowab.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2.9 \xt Lo 1.17\x*Koęž‰sega giyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, noloęž‰ dianilalega, Godeyaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰yoęž‰ gi oęž‰goęž‰saki, ge mogagoęž‰ dowab.
\v 10 \x - \xo 2.10 \xt Wkp 19.37, Nam 20.7-12,24, Madi 5.19\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰yoęž‰ tambo kudu haęž‰naki, ele imilise nowoęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰salega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ ele saefaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo oęž‰goęž‰sanoęž‰ aęž‰ngab.
\v 11 \x - \xo 2.11 \xt Kis 20.13-14, Lom 13.9\x*Aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰woęž‰ we. Gode imilise eyoęž‰ ele aęž‰laęž‰ we e saefaęž‰. Nowoęž‰ â€śgayoęž‰ afa diaęž‰soęž‰bo.â€ť Nowoęž‰ â€śkalu nowoęž‰ sana sowaęž‰soęž‰bo,â€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ E saefaęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ gayoęž‰ moęž‰afa diaki, kaluwoęž‰ sana sowalega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ele saefaęž‰loęž‰ oęž‰goęž‰san kalu dowab.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 2.12 \xt Gala 6.2, Yaęž‰m 1.25, 1Bid 2.16\x*Tif amioęž‰ nioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ alobaęž‰dalikiyoęž‰, gaęž‰li meseaęž‰kiloęž‰ fase alifaęž‰ ele aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nioęž‰ alobaęž‰maęž‰ib. Gioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ asulufoęž‰likiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gili man dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ to saęž‰lan oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaęž‰bi.
\v 13 \x - \xo 2.13 \xt Madi 5.7, 18.32-35\x*Moęž‰woęž‰ kalu abeyoęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ moęž‰nofolaęž‰lalega, tif amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ kalu emoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰nofolaki, halaidoęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega kalu abeyoęž‰ noloęž‰ nofoloęž‰ alitaęž‰senoęž‰lalega, moęž‰walilab aęž‰namioęž‰ e gaęž‰li domaęž‰ib.
\s1 Tilidabu oęž‰liaęž‰ man dimidan oęž‰liaęž‰ alobaęž‰dan
\p 
\v 14 Ni mili gioęž‰, kalu abeyoęž‰ â€śNe Keliso amioęž‰ tili doęž‰doęž‰lkaęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰li koęž‰sega, eyoęž‰ man nafayoęž‰ moęž‰dimidaęž‰senoęž‰lalega, tilidabu oęž‰leoęž‰ngoęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰li asuwaęž‰faęž‰ibaęž‰le? Tilidabu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleyoęž‰ mada moęž‰gasiliaęž‰ib.
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 2.15-16 \xt 1Yoęž‰n 3.17\x*Keliso kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ tilidabu kalukaęž‰isale nowoęž‰ maęž‰noęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰ soęž‰g oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ aundoęž‰ma baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, â€śHaęž‰iyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ soęž‰g oęž‰liaęž‰ maęž‰n oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gemoęž‰woęž‰ dimiaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰ ge haęž‰sa taęž‰biâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nofoloęž‰ towoęž‰ saęž‰laki koęž‰sega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰asuwaęž‰talega, eyoęž‰ kalu oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ man nafayoęž‰ moęž‰dimidab. To eloęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ e waga asuwaęž‰faęž‰iba?
\v 17 Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ tilidabu mosowoęž‰ e amioęž‰ aęž‰lab koęž‰sega man nafa dimidanoęž‰ e amioęž‰ moęž‰faęž‰laęž‰dowalega, tilidabu eloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 2.18 \xt Gala 5.6\x*Koęž‰sega kalu nomaęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śKalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ noloęž‰ man nafa dimidanoęž‰ aęž‰labâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Koęž‰sega niyoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰, â€śGe man nafa dimidanoęž‰ aundoęž‰malalega, tilidabu giloęž‰woęž‰ waga walamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰? Koęž‰sega man nafa koęž‰loęž‰ niloęž‰ dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, tilidabu niloęž‰woęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widakigabâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰maęž‰noęž‰.
\v 19 Godeyoęž‰ imilig koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ giyoęž‰ tilidaęž‰dab. Aęž‰noęž‰ nafa koęž‰sega, mama mogagoęž‰ iyoęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰ka tili asulakiyoęž‰, iyoęž‰ tagilaki bibisodaęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 20 Ge babale dowab koęž‰loęž‰, ge fanda asulumaęž‰ki walamaęž‰nigoęž‰l. Tilidabu moso iliki man nafayoęž‰ aundoęž‰malalega, tilidabu aęž‰noęž‰ hendele oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowab.
\v 21 \x - \xo 2.21 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 22.9-12\x*Nili maęž‰mu Ablaham e asuluma. Ene soęž‰wa Aisaęž‰goęž‰ u dibidoęž‰ waęž‰la diaęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, Godemoęž‰ dimi koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ eloęž‰ dimidab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, e mada digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰.
\v 22 \x - \xo 2.22 \xt Hibu 11.17-18\x*Ene tilidabu oęž‰liaęž‰ man eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ idaęž‰ni gasayabiki, eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ ene tilidabuwoęž‰ aęž‰na ilili alifaęž‰.
\v 23 \x - \xo 2.23 \xt Moęž‰moęž‰ 15.6, 2Sto 20.7, Ais 41.8\x*Tamin amioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ amioęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰, â€śAblaham e Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ to saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ hendele tilidaęž‰dabiki, Gode eyoęž‰ e digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na saefaęž‰.â€ť Aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ Ablaham eyoęž‰ ene soęž‰wayoęž‰ dimiab amioęž‰, to aęž‰noęž‰ ilili alifaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śAblaham we noęž‰noęž‰n milile dowabâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰.
\v 24 Gioęž‰ asuluma. Tilidabu moso dowab aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge digaloęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰maęž‰ib. Tilidabu oęž‰liaęž‰ man nafale dimidab oęž‰liaęž‰ gasayalikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ ge digaloęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ aęž‰na saefaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 2.25 \xt Jos 2.1-21, Hibu 11.31\x*Oęž‰leaumboęž‰ uwoęž‰ diakiloęž‰ moleloęž‰ diaęž‰sen ga, Lehab eyoęž‰ oęž‰lusendoęž‰ mioęž‰ kalu aęž‰laęž‰ nowoęž‰ e boęž‰foęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰, gis kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ moęž‰sanamaęž‰ki, kalu aęž‰laęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tog nowa iligaęž‰foęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, eloęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ baęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ Lehab e digaloęž‰ kaęž‰isale aęž‰laęž‰saefaęž‰.
\v 26 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu mamaloęž‰ma dowab aęž‰noęž‰ e sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, e sowoęž‰ oęž‰leaumboęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ tilidabu mosowoęž‰ dowaki, man nafa dimidanoęž‰ aundoęž‰malalega, kalu aęž‰maęž‰ tilidabuwoęž‰ sowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\c 3
\s1 Megoęž‰foęž‰ tilidowaęž‰bi
\p 
\v 1 Ni mili gioęž‰, Godeyaęž‰ toloęž‰ widan kaluwoęž‰ modoęž‰ domaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ asulaęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ tif amioęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ widan kalu nioęž‰ mada halaidoęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰ib.
\v 2 Nioęž‰ tambowaęž‰yoęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidaęž‰lowan. Koęž‰sega, kalu imilise nowoęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰ dinafa tilidowaki, halayoęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰lalega, e mada digaloęž‰ kalu dowab koęž‰loęž‰, ene doęž‰moęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ man dimidan aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ tambo oęž‰li tilidomaęž‰ib.
\p 
\v 3 Hoęž‰soęž‰ nilidoęž‰ asulab au toga hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, goęž‰foęž‰ ki haęž‰lu nowoęž‰ hoęž‰s aęž‰maęž‰ megoęž‰fa disalitaęž‰gaęž‰, susululab amioęž‰, hoęž‰soęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au haęž‰naęž‰sen. Hoęž‰saęž‰ ene doęž‰moęž‰ alan aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ goęž‰foęž‰ ki haęž‰lu aęž‰maęž‰ tililiaęž‰ haęž‰nan.
\v 4 Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ hoęž‰n koęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰ soęž‰lu hoęž‰n waęž‰l amiloęž‰ haęž‰nanoęž‰ asuluma. Hoęž‰n koęž‰suwoęž‰ alan badioęž‰ kelegoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ fufa alanaęž‰ aniliaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰sen. Koęž‰sega kelegoęž‰ haęž‰lu, hoęž‰n koęž‰suwoęž‰ hamanaęž‰kiloęž‰ dehegan aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ hoęž‰n koęž‰su alan aęž‰noęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, hoęž‰n koęž‰suloęž‰ bisoęž‰waęž‰loęž‰ asulab au haęž‰naęž‰sen.
\v 5 Oęž‰leaumboęž‰, kaluwaęž‰ doęž‰moęž‰ amioęž‰, eanoęž‰ haęž‰lulaęž‰su koęž‰loęž‰lab, koęž‰sega to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ kailakiyoęž‰, towoęž‰ alan saęž‰laęž‰sen. \fig Hoęž‰soęž‰ nilidoęž‰ asulab au toga hamanaęž‰kiyoęž‰, goęž‰foęž‰ kiyoęž‰ hoęž‰saęž‰ megoęž‰fa disalitaęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰sen.|alt="Sarah riding her horse" src="09-05-19 114b_gr.tif" size="col" copy="Sylvia Grosh (SIL)" ref="3.3"\fig*
\p Nioęž‰ asulumaęž‰niki. De kaęž‰si haęž‰lulaęž‰su aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ henaęž‰ usa ti alilab amioęž‰, hen aęž‰namiloęž‰ i aęž‰noęž‰ tambo deyaęž‰ tandalemaęž‰ib.
\v 6 \x - \xo 3.6 \xt Madi 12.36-37, 15.11,18-19\x*Eanoęž‰ de oęž‰ngoęž‰ dowoęž‰. De aęž‰noęž‰ de hena aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, de aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ kaluwaęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ tambo mogagaęž‰i haęž‰nab koęž‰loęž‰, nililoęž‰ aęž‰ tilidomaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰. To nililoęž‰ saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ nili asuloęž‰ us amiloęž‰ delen aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ widakigab. To saęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili asuloęž‰woęž‰ tambo heyoęž‰ dowaęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 3.7-8 \xt Lom 3.13\x*Noęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰woęž‰, kaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰, oęž‰baęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰, kaluwaęž‰yoęž‰ fofakiyoęž‰ dinafa tilidomaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ oęž‰li koęž‰sega, kalukaęž‰isale imilig nomaęž‰yoęž‰ eanoęž‰ moęž‰tilidomaęž‰ib. Ean aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ alan dimidaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, kisaęž‰waęž‰l aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ omaęž‰nikiloęž‰ dimidalian aęž‰ngab.
\p 
\v 9 Nili megoęž‰f amioęž‰ ean aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ nili Do Gode Alanaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale ene misidoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ mogagimaęž‰kiyoęž‰ tolaęž‰sen.
\v 10 Ean nililoęž‰woęž‰ to saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, to nafayoęž‰loęž‰, to mogagoęž‰woęž‰loęž‰, megoęž‰f imilig aęž‰naka sahandalowaęž‰lab. Ni mili, nioęž‰ man we oęž‰ngoęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰ililoęž‰.
\v 11-12 Alonaęž‰ i amioęž‰ ukayoęž‰ hedanoęž‰? Bosalaęž‰ me amioęž‰ alonoęž‰ hedanoęž‰?\f + \fr 3.11-12 \ft Yaęž‰maęž‰s eyoęž‰ uka fo oęž‰liaęž‰ bosalaęž‰ me oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰laki, oęž‰lif oęž‰liaęž‰ wainaęž‰ me oęž‰liaęž‰ aęž‰na daęž‰fe sioęž‰.\f* Aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰gan. Ni mili, hoęž‰n nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ hoęž‰n oęž‰toęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰, hoęž‰n si imilig amioęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowanoęž‰? Hoęž‰n si mogagoęž‰ aęž‰namioęž‰, hoęž‰n nafayoęž‰ mada moęž‰faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.
\s1 Asuloęž‰ nafayoęž‰ Godeloęž‰wa aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ yan
\p 
\v 13 Gi usamioęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ man nafa oęž‰liaęž‰ mogagoęž‰ oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dinafa fanda asululi aęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰laba? Noloęž‰ aęž‰laboęž‰lalega, e nolbaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowakiloęž‰, ene man digaloęž‰le dimidaęž‰lab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, asuloęž‰ eloęž‰ di aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ walamaęž‰ib.
\v 14 Koęž‰sega gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ etean man oęž‰liaęž‰ waęž‰la saęž‰ndan man oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ dowalega, man aęž‰noęž‰ digaęž‰daki, goęž‰noęž‰n wi aęž‰noęž‰ duludakiyoęž‰ dikidaęž‰soęž‰bo.
\v 15 Moęž‰woęž‰ man aęž‰noęž‰ Hebene aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ mioęž‰ma. Man aęž‰noęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wemaęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kaluwaęž‰ asuloęž‰ us aęž‰naka faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰lab. Ene iyayoęž‰ Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰.
\v 16 Etean man oęž‰liaęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ asulan man oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale us amioęž‰ dowalega, aęž‰laęž‰iyan man oęž‰liaęž‰ man mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ noloęž‰ aęž‰na dofoęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 17 Koęž‰sega asuloęž‰ nafa koęž‰loęž‰ Hebene halona aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ tambo goęž‰goęž‰doęž‰ maliloęž‰le dowoęž‰. Kalukaęž‰isale asuloęž‰ nafa oęž‰loęž‰ di aęž‰maęž‰ manoęž‰ we. Haęž‰sa dowaęž‰sen, haęž‰faęž‰nolo dowaęž‰sen, kalu nomaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰sen, nowoęž‰ nofolaęž‰sen, aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ man nafa dimidaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ alan dowaęž‰sen. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ nafale aęž‰laęž‰ alobaęž‰dakiyoęž‰, noloęž‰ moęž‰dianilaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ moęž‰dikili saęž‰laęž‰sen.
\v 18 \x - \xo 3.18 \xt Madi 5.9, Hibu 12.11\x*Kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ noloęž‰ haęž‰sa meseaęž‰ki, haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lakiloęž‰ man nafa dimidab aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰lan man aęž‰noęž‰ e gelan aęž‰ngab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ tif amioęž‰ hende hedan aumboęž‰, man digaloęž‰le aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ib.
\c 4
\s1 Gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi
\p 
\v 1 \x - \xo 4.1 \xt Lom 7.23\x*Gi usamiloęž‰ towaęž‰loęž‰ halaidoęž‰ kegaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, oęž‰ba aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowaba? Mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ kele asuloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰, gili asuloęž‰ usamioęž‰ tadowoęž‰labiki, aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰lab.
\v 2 Giliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ noloęž‰ alan asulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰dialikiyoęž‰, kalu nowoęž‰ sana somaęž‰noęž‰ asulan. Giliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ noloęž‰ meselaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ moęž‰dialikiyoęž‰, towaęž‰yoęž‰ kegaki buban. Giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dabu baęž‰baęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, kelegoęž‰ gililoęž‰ asulab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰sen.
\v 3 Giliyoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dabu baęž‰dab amioęž‰, gililoęž‰ haęž‰iyab aęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰diaęž‰sen. Moęž‰woęž‰ giliyoęž‰ hala asulaki, gininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ sagalemaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ dabu baęž‰dabiki, Gode eyoęž‰ gimoęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰dimiaęž‰sen.
\p 
\v 4 \x - \xo 4.4 \xt Lom 8.7, 1Yoęž‰n 2.15\x*Gayoęž‰ kaluwoęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ inoęž‰ taęž‰takiloęž‰ uwoęž‰ diaęž‰li sian oęž‰leaumboęž‰ gili dimidaęž‰lab. Kalu abeyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ manoęž‰ mada alan asulaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, e Gode oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dimidaęž‰lab, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰asulaya? Hendele, kalu abeyoęž‰ henfeloęž‰ man we oęž‰liaęž‰ ege dowalega, e Gode oęž‰liaęž‰ gis diab.
\v 5 Godeyaęž‰ bugoęž‰ us amiloęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰, â€śGode eyoęž‰ nili mamayoęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo enedoęž‰ asulab au kudu yaęž‰meleaęž‰kiyoęž‰, alan asulab.â€ť To aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ sioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ma.
\v 6 \x - \xo 4.6 \xt Sndn 3.34, 1Bid 5.5\x*Koęž‰sega Gode eyoęž‰ nimoęž‰woęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ alan disaęž‰laki, nioęž‰ asuwaęž‰taęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰gaęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ ene to saęž‰saęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰sioęž‰,
\q1 â€śGode eyoęž‰ kalu abeyoęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ kailaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ gis dowab.
\q2 Koęž‰sega eyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale abeyoęž‰ ininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰g amiloęž‰ dowab i aęž‰noęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ haęž‰foęž‰ disaęž‰laki, nafale meseaęž‰ki taęž‰taęž‰sen.â€ť
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 4.7 \xt Aęž‰fe 6.12\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ asulab au dimidaki, e haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi. Gioęž‰ halale kagayaki, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ e gola baęž‰daęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, Saęž‰daęž‰naęž‰ eyoęž‰ ge taęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰, e nai haęž‰naęž‰ib.
\v 8 \x - \xo 4.8 \xt Ais 1.16, Sek 1.3, Mal 3.7\x*Gioęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ anibdeya haęž‰naęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, Gode eloęž‰ gi oęž‰liaęž‰ anibdeya domaęž‰ miaęž‰ib. Man mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰lab kalu gioęž‰, dagi heyoęž‰ toęž‰goęž‰dan oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gioęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ tambo taęž‰taęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ asuloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰lab gioęž‰, mogagoęž‰ asulan aęž‰noęž‰ kataęž‰taki, kufaęž‰ usoęž‰ maliloęž‰ dowaęž‰bi.
\v 9 Gililoęž‰ hala dimidaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ asulakiyoęž‰, nofolaki yaęž‰laęž‰lubi. Gioęž‰ sagalaęž‰likiloęž‰ oęž‰gaęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ nodolaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, kele asulakiyoęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\v 10 \x - \xo 4.10 \xt Job 5.11, 1Bid 5.6\x*Gioęž‰ wiloęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowaki, Alanaęž‰ haęž‰ga dowaęž‰bi. Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ iwalu dulugu alifaęž‰ib.
\s1 Gao nomaęž‰loęž‰ dimidaboęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo
\p 
\v 11 Ni milile, giliyoęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ noloęž‰ sadaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo. Kalu abeyoęž‰ ao nomaęž‰ man dimidaboęž‰ alobana baęž‰daki sadaęž‰dalega, kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ ele difaęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ alobana baęž‰daki, oęž‰ngoęž‰maloęž‰ngoęž‰ dowakigab. Giyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, ge ele aęž‰maęž‰ haęž‰g amioęž‰ moęž‰dowaki, ge moęž‰walilan kalu oęž‰ngoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowab.
\v 12 \x - \xo 4.12 \xt Lom 2.1, 14.4\x*Eleyoęž‰ Gode imilise ene saefaęž‰. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalukaęž‰isaleloęž‰ moęž‰walilaęž‰sen aęž‰noęž‰ Gode imilise e koęž‰loęž‰lab. Kalukaęž‰isale noloęž‰ aęž‰gasiliaki, noloęž‰ yasalaki, aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Gode e amioęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰lab. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu noloęž‰ giloęž‰ alobaęž‰daęž‰labko, ge mada oęž‰boęž‰ngoęž‰woęž‰?
\s1 Kailan manoęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰bi
\p 
\v 13 \x - \xo 4.13 \xt Luk 12.18-20\x*Kalu abeyoęž‰ enenaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ kailakiyoęž‰, â€śAliyoęž‰ ne amisaęž‰n nowa haęž‰naęž‰gaęž‰, dona imilise nowoęž‰ aęž‰na siliki nanog diaęž‰likiyoęž‰, moleyoęž‰ alan diaęž‰noęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰doęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰sen gioęž‰, ni to we dabuma.
\v 14 \x - \xo 4.14 \xt Song 39.5,11, Sndn 27.1\x*Hendele, gioęž‰ aliloęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab ko moęž‰asuloęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab. Gi amiloęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰ daęž‰lab ko, maęž‰noęž‰ ufaęž‰ amiloęž‰ ho faęž‰laęž‰dowaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ boęž‰e kelegelian oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\v 15 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ moęž‰saęž‰laki, we au saęž‰laęž‰bi. â€śKalu Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidamaęž‰ki asulalega, ne oęž‰silikiyoęž‰, nanog nol we oęž‰dimidaęž‰melaęž‰noęž‰â€ť giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰saęž‰laęž‰bi.
\v 16 Koęž‰sega gioęž‰ goęž‰noęž‰naęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ kailaki, goęž‰noęž‰n wiyoęž‰ duludaęž‰sen. Goęž‰noęž‰ndoęž‰ kailan man aęž‰noęž‰ mada mogagoęž‰le koęž‰loęž‰lab.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 4.17 \xt Luk 12.47\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ kalu abeyoęž‰ man nafale dimidamaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ e asuloęž‰ koęž‰sega moęž‰dimidalega, kalu aęž‰noęž‰ mogagoęž‰le dimidab.
\c 5
\s1 Kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalumoęž‰woęž‰ hagugu sioęž‰
\p 
\v 1 Kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰loęž‰ daęž‰lab kalu gioęž‰ dinafa dabuma. Gi amioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰ alanoęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰nigab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰ modaki yaęž‰laęž‰lubi.
\v 2 \x - \xo 5.2 \xt Madi 6.19\x*Kelegoęž‰ nafa gililoęž‰woęž‰ abulaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰, gegede ane koęž‰m. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ helebesoęž‰g nafale gililoęž‰ daęž‰lab ko walibiayaęž‰ tandalaęž‰.
\v 3 Gili moleyoęž‰, goęž‰l oęž‰liaęž‰ silba oęž‰liaęž‰yoęž‰ wameleli koęž‰m. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰walilab amioęž‰, wameloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gililoęž‰ hala dimidan aęž‰noęž‰ kalaba walamaęž‰ib koęž‰loęž‰, wameloęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ gi doęž‰moęž‰ ko, deyaęž‰loęž‰ nan aumaęž‰ib. Hoęž‰len we elemaęž‰nigab koęž‰sega giliyoęž‰ kelegoęž‰ modoęž‰woęž‰ ka kegenelaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lab.
\v 4 \x - \xo 5.4 \xt Lo 24.14-15\x*Dabuma! Giliyoęž‰ egeloęž‰ amiloęž‰ nanogdoęž‰ dian kalu iyoęž‰ moleyoęž‰ moęž‰kilili koęž‰loęž‰, mole moęž‰kililiakiloęž‰ taęž‰li aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, gililoęž‰ hala dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ kalaba widaki hoęž‰idab. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gili nanogdoęž‰ dian kaluwaęž‰loęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, Alan Halaidoęž‰leloęž‰ Aęž‰lab eyoęž‰ oęž‰ma dabu.
\p 
\v 5 \x - \xo 5.5 \xt Luk 16.25\x*Gioęž‰ henfeloęž‰ wena silikiyoęž‰, kelegoęž‰woęž‰ gililoęž‰ asulab au kegene dilaęž‰likiyoęž‰, hoęž‰lenoęž‰ tambo gininaęž‰maęž‰laęž‰yoęž‰ sagalaęž‰sen. Kabowoęž‰ todaęž‰liliab amiloęž‰ saęž‰mbaęž‰ni haęž‰nab oęž‰leaumboęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ Godeyaęž‰loęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰domaęž‰ni haęž‰nab.
\v 6 Giliyoęž‰ kalukaęž‰isale halaloęž‰ moęž‰dimidoęž‰ noloęž‰ moęž‰walilaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰ sana sowaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ gililoęž‰ dimidab aęž‰namioęž‰ iliyoęž‰ moęž‰galalaęž‰sen.
\s1 Hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ giloęž‰wa faęž‰laęž‰dowalikiyoęž‰, haęž‰sa siliki, halaidoęž‰ dowaęž‰bi
\p 
\v 7 \x - \xo 5.7 \xt Lo 11.14, Jer 5.24\x*Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ ni mili, gioęž‰ Alandoęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ haęž‰sa iliki yasilaęž‰lubi. Gioęž‰ asuluma, egeloęž‰loęž‰ bisoęž‰waęž‰yoęž‰ fowoęž‰ gelaęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, hoęž‰n timaęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰sa iliki yasilaęž‰sen. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ fo tumaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰len aęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ yasilaęž‰likiyoęž‰, e haęž‰sa sen.
\v 8 \x - \xo 5.8 \xt Lom 13.11-12, 1Bid 4.7\x*Oęž‰leaumboęž‰, Alandoęž‰ miaęž‰nigab aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma dowab koęž‰loęž‰, gioęž‰loęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dowaki, haęž‰sa iliki yasilaęž‰lubi.
\v 9 Ni mili, giliyoęž‰ gao nowoęž‰mboęž‰woęž‰ moęž‰beakiyoęž‰ sadaęž‰daęž‰soęž‰bo. Moęž‰woęž‰ giliyoęž‰ aęž‰laęž‰dimidalega, Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰walilimaęž‰ib. Boęž‰ba! Moęž‰walilimaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ kalu aęž‰noęž‰ togaęž‰ meya kagafoęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, moęž‰walilimaęž‰noęž‰ hoęž‰lenoęž‰ koęž‰naęž‰ma faęž‰laęž‰dowab.
\p 
\v 10 Ni mili, Godeyaęž‰ dinali saęž‰lan kalu iyoęž‰, Alanaęž‰ wiya aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ widab amioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ diaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰lalikiyoęž‰, halaidoęž‰ dowaki, haęž‰sa elen. Gioęž‰ ililoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ oęž‰leau, haęž‰sa iliki kudu haęž‰naęž‰bi.
\v 11 \x - \xo 5.11 \xt Kis 34.6, Job 1.21-22, 2.10, Song 103.8\x*Hidaęž‰yoęž‰loęž‰ diaęž‰i haęž‰naęž‰len kalukaęž‰isale aęž‰noęž‰ wabulun dowab aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ nioęž‰ asuloęž‰. Yoęž‰b e amioęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ faęž‰laęž‰dowabikiyoęž‰, e halaidoęž‰ kagafoęž‰liki haęž‰sa elen koęž‰loęž‰, tif amioęž‰ Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ e sagale alitaki ilili alifaęž‰. Maloloęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gioęž‰ daęž‰daęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰ asuloęž‰. Hendele, Alan eyoęž‰ nofolakiloęž‰ asuwaęž‰tan man aęž‰noęž‰, e amioęž‰ waęž‰lifoęž‰.
\p 
\v 12 \x - \xo 5.12 \xt Madi 5.34-37\x*Ni mili, to waęž‰laęž‰b daęž‰laboęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ saęž‰maęž‰nigoęž‰l. Giliyoęž‰ elelaęž‰ saęž‰lan aumboęž‰, Hebene wi amiyaęž‰le, henfeloęž‰ wi amiyaęž‰le, moęž‰ wi no amiyaęž‰le aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ mada saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ moęž‰walilabenaęž‰ki, aęž‰laęž‰boęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰soęž‰bo. Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ giliyoęž‰ dinali saęž‰lakiyoęž‰, â€śAęž‰â€ť aęž‰laęž‰ka saęž‰laęž‰bi, moęž‰ â€śAâ€ť aęž‰laęž‰ka saęž‰laęž‰bi.
\s1 Godemoęž‰loęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ halaidoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰lab
\p 
\v 13 Kalukaęž‰isale gi usamioęž‰ nowoęž‰ hidaęž‰yoęž‰woęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, e Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰bi. Kalukaęž‰isale gi usamioęž‰ nowoęž‰ sagalalikiyoęž‰, e Godeyaęž‰ wiyoęž‰ duludaki, sagaloęž‰ gisaloęž‰woęž‰ saęž‰laęž‰bi.
\v 14 \x - \xo 5.14 \xt Mak 6.13\x*Kalukaęž‰isale gi usamioęž‰ nowoęž‰ walafoęž‰ dowalikiyoęž‰, eyoęž‰ saęž‰sdoęž‰ boęž‰foęž‰lowan kaluwoęž‰ eloęž‰wa menaęž‰ki hoęž‰idaęž‰bi. Iliyoęž‰ wa hoęž‰noęž‰ e waęž‰la tulaki, Alanaęž‰ wi amioęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu samaęž‰ki, hoęž‰idaęž‰bi.
\v 15 \x - \xo 5.15 \xt Madi 17.18-20\x*Aęž‰laęž‰dimidalikiyoęž‰, ililoęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, walaf kalu aęž‰noęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰ falele alitabiki, Alanaęž‰yoęž‰ e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dasi alifaęž‰ib. Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰ mogagoęž‰woęž‰ dimidoęž‰lalega, Gode eyoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ halaliki gaęž‰lilaęž‰maęž‰ib.
\v 16 Aęž‰laęž‰foęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ Gode eyoęž‰ gioęž‰ falele alifomaęž‰kiyoęž‰, gililoęž‰ mogagoęž‰ dimidoęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ fogaęž‰le saęž‰laęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰yoęž‰, giliyoęž‰ gegeleboęž‰ nowoęž‰ Godemoęž‰ dulugu saęž‰laęž‰lubi. Kalu Gode amiloęž‰ tilidaęž‰daęž‰saęž‰gaęž‰loęž‰ digaloęž‰ dowab aęž‰maęž‰loęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰, halaidoęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰lab koęž‰loęž‰, eloęž‰ dulugu saęž‰lab aęž‰noęž‰ hendele asuwaęž‰taęž‰sen.
\p 
\v 17 \x - \xo 5.17 \xt 1Kin 17.1, 18.1\x*Elaiya e ni oęž‰ngoęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, eyoęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰timenaęž‰ki, Godemoęž‰woęž‰ halaidoęž‰ dulugu sioęž‰ koęž‰loęž‰, dona otalen aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ ele doęž‰goęž‰felaęž‰foęž‰ us aęž‰namioęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ moęž‰tiaęž‰.
\v 18 \x - \xo 5.18 \xt 1Kin 18.42-45\x*Aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ Elaiya eyoęž‰ hoęž‰noęž‰ aęž‰timenaęž‰kiyoęž‰, Godemoęž‰ waęž‰ka dulugu saęž‰labiki, hoęž‰noęž‰ akin halona aęž‰laęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ tindabiki, egeloęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰na faęž‰laęž‰ne.
\p 
\v 19-20 \x - \xo 5.19-20 \xt Gala 6.1\x*\x - \xo 5.19-20 \xt Sndn 10.12, 1Bid 4.8\x*Ni mili, gi us amioęž‰ kalu imilig nowoęž‰ Godeyaęž‰ to hendele aęž‰noęž‰ kataęž‰taęž‰gaęž‰ haęž‰nabiki, kalu nomaęž‰yoęž‰ e aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ tililiaęž‰ mioęž‰lalega, kalu aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, to we asuluma. Kalu abeyoęž‰, ao nowoęž‰ mogagoęž‰loęž‰ dimidaęž‰li haęž‰naęž‰len koęž‰loęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ tililiaęž‰ mioęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰yoęž‰, kalu somaęž‰noęž‰loęž‰ dobaęž‰daęž‰loęž‰ haęž‰naęž‰len oęž‰moęž‰woęž‰ melaęž‰noęž‰woęž‰ aęž‰maęž‰laęž‰ dimi. Aęž‰laęž‰goęž‰koęž‰loęž‰ mogagoęž‰ koęž‰li koęž‰liloęž‰ dimidaęž‰li mioęž‰ aęž‰noęž‰ Godeyoęž‰ moęž‰boęž‰baęž‰ki, goęž‰lu alifaęž‰. 
